      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "faq_1_answer",
      "label": "Answer",
      "default": "You know that loud wind noise you experience at high speeds? Being exposed to that for even as little as 10 minutes can lead to that dreaded ear ringing. Which is not only annoying but leads to permanent hearing damage if repeated over time. Also called tinnitus it is something unfortunately too many experienced riders struggle with. That is why it's our mission to prevent that permanent ear ringing by providing the most rider friendly earplugs on the market."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Question 2"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
